Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients, signature (6,-15,20,-15,6,-1).
formula: E.g.f. for homeomorphically irreducible multigraphs with n nodes and k edges is (1 + x*y)^( - 1/2)*exp(x*y/2 + x^2*y^2/4)*Sum_{k >= 0} 1/(1 - x)^binomial(k, 2)*exp( - x^2*y*k^2/(2*(1 + x*y)) - x^2*y*k/2)*y^k/k!.
